<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Writing — Eugene Chetty</title>
<meta name="description" content="Articles on marketing leadership, digital strategy, and the translator problem in regulated industries.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg-dark: #080E0D; --bg-light: #F5F7F6; --bg-mid: #ECF0EF;
  --text-dark: #0A0F0E; --text-light: #EEF4F3;
  --accent: #0A7A6A; --accent-light: #0DA08C;
  --text-secondary: #6B7876; --text-secondary-light: #8FA49F;
  --border: #D8E2E0; --border-dark: #152320;
  --font-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; --font-body: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
}
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { font-family: var(--font-body); background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-dark); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  padding: 22px 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  background: rgba(8,14,13,0.97); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dark); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
}
.nav-name { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-light); text-decoration: none; }
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; list-style: none; }
.nav-links a { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-secondary-light); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; }
.nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: var(--text-light); }

.writing-hero { padding: 140px 48px 72px; background: var(--bg-dark); }
.writing-hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
.hero-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; }
.hero-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(44px, 6vw, 80px); font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.06; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.hero-sub { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-secondary-light); max-width: 480px; line-height: 1.7; }

.articles-section { padding: 72px 48px 100px; }
.articles-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }

.articles-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2px; }

.article-card {
  background: var(--bg-light); padding: 40px 36px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  text-decoration: none; min-height: 260px;
  transition: background 0.2s; border: none;
}
.article-card:hover { background: #fff; }
.article-card:nth-child(1) { background: var(--bg-dark); }
.article-card:nth-child(1):hover { background: #111816; }
.article-card:nth-child(1) .article-title { color: var(--text-light); }
.article-card:nth-child(1) .article-meta { color: var(--text-secondary-light); }
.article-card:nth-child(1) .article-summary { color: var(--text-secondary-light); }

.article-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.article-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.25; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.article-summary { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: auto; padding-bottom: 20px; flex: 1; }
.article-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-top: auto; display: flex; gap: 12px; }
.meta-dot { width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--border); align-self: center; }

.empty-state { padding: 80px 0; text-align: center; }
.empty-state p { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; }
.empty-state strong { font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-dark); }

footer { background: var(--bg-dark); border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dark); padding: 28px 48px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
.footer-name { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary-light); }
.footer-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; list-style: none; }
.footer-links a { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary-light); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.07em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; }
.footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text-light); }

@media (max-width: 960px) {
  nav { padding: 20px 24px; }
  .nav-links { display: none; }
  .writing-hero { padding: 120px 24px 56px; }
  .articles-section { padding: 48px 24px 72px; }
  .articles-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  footer { padding: 24px; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-name">Eugene Chetty</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/#thesis">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="/writing" class="active">Writing</a></li>
    <li><a href="/#lab">Lab</a></li>
    <li><a href="/#connect">Connect</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<div class="writing-hero">
  <div class="writing-hero-inner">
    <span class="hero-label">How I think</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Writing</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">On marketing leadership, digital strategy, and the translator problem in regulated industries.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="articles-section">
  <div class="articles-inner">
    {% if collections.articles.length > 0 %}
    <div class="articles-grid">
      {% for article in collections.articles %}
      <a href="{{ article.url }}" class="article-card">
        <div class="article-tag">{{ article.data.tag }}</div>
        <h2 class="article-title">{{ article.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="article-summary">{{ article.data.summary }}</p>
        <div class="article-meta">
          <span>{{ article.data.date | dateDisplay }}</span>
          <div class="meta-dot"></div>
          <span>{{ article.data.readtime }}</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="empty-state">
      <p>Articles are on their way.<br><strong>First up:</strong> Why energy companies keep hiring the wrong marketers.</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-name">Eugene Chetty &mdash; Wellington, NZ</div>
  <ul class="footer-links">
    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="/writing">Writing</a></li>
    <li><a href="/#lab">Lab</a></li>
    <li><a href="mailto:hello@eugenechetty.com">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
